---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Simulation and Forecasting | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="Scenario intelligence, forecasting, and simulation tools for policy, infrastructure, climate, energy, and economic decisions."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Simulation and Forecasting
      </p>
      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        Explore futures before they happen.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI combines forecasting, simulation, and AI-assisted interpretation to help organisations test assumptions, compare scenarios, and understand future risks.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            The problem
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Strategic decisions require a view of what may change.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Policy, infrastructure, energy, climate, and economic decisions often depend on uncertain future conditions. Demand may shift, costs may change, hazards may intensify, and communities may respond in different ways.
          </p>
          <p>
            Simulation and forecasting tools help decision-makers test assumptions before committing resources. PrincipalAI adds an intelligence layer that helps users interpret results, compare scenarios, and translate model outputs into decision-ready insight.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          What it supports
        </p>
        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Forecasting and simulation for decisions under uncertainty.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Scenario design</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Define alternative futures, policy settings, demand assumptions, cost pathways, and intervention options.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Forecast interpretation</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Turn forecast results into clear explanations of drivers, sensitivities, risks, and implications.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Model interaction</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Help users interrogate model outputs, compare assumptions, and understand why results differ.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Decision reporting</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Generate structured summaries for planning, investment, policy advice, and governance papers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Example applications
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Built for the questions that matter before decisions are made.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            How do outcomes change under different growth, cost, or climate assumptions?
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Which scenarios create the greatest exposure to fiscal, operational, or social risk?
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            What assumptions are driving the difference between low, medium, and high forecasts?
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Which intervention pathways are most robust across uncertain futures?
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            AI that works with models, not around them.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            PrincipalAI’s simulation and forecasting capability is designed for analytical environments where assumptions, evidence, and model structure matter.
          </p>
          <p>
            We combine AI with applied modelling experience across economics, infrastructure, transport, climate, energy, health, and spatial analysis, helping organisations move from outputs to decisions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Test assumptions before they become commitments.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about forecasting, scenario intelligence, and AI-assisted simulation for complex decisions.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
